parts.text:
Slurm

```json
{
  "software": [
    "Slurm",
    "Singularity",
    "Dask",
    "Python"
  ],
  "resources": {
    "hpc_config_file": {
      "variables": [
        "HPC_SLURM_ACCOUNT",
        "HPC_SLURM_TIME",
        "HPC_SLURM_NUM_NODES",
        "HPC_SLURM_CPUS_PER_NODE",
        "HPC_SLURM_MEM_PER_CPU",
        "HPC_MASTER_WORKERS",
        "HPC_MASTER_GPU"
      ]
    },
    "singularity_image": "singularity/ubuntu_warehouse.sif",
    "logging_directory": "slurm_logs/slurm_{DATE}",
    "scheduler_file": "{LOGDIR}/scheduler_info.json",
    "experiment_script": "env_search/main.py",
    "config_file": "{CONFIG}",
    "project_directory": "/project"
  },
  "flags": [
    "-d (dry run)",
    "-r LOGDIR (reload from an existing logging directory)"
  ]
}
```
